# Import Order

## TypeScript/Vue

```typescript
// 1. External dependencies
import { ref, computed } from "vue";
import { storeToRefs } from "pinia";

// 2. Internal dependencies (use @/* alias)
import { useSelectionStore } from "@/composables";
import { validateBounds } from "@/utils/validation";
import { isLayer } from "@/utils/typeGuards";
import { safeNumber } from "@/utils/numericSafety";

// 3. Relative dependencies
import type { LayerConfig } from "./types";
```

Type exports: Grouped in separate `export type {}` blocks.

